{
  "texts": [
    "The average episodic rewards are displayed using a moving average with a window size of 50.",
    "All runs use the identical molecular scaffold filter.",
    "For both PPO and A2C, Top current gives the lowest average episodic reward, as shown in Fig. 6a and b, respectively.",
    "Furthermore, PPO utilizing Bin current and All current performs on par, giving moving averages between 0.8 and 0.7 after roughly 125 episodes.",
    "It seems that most replay buffers converge after around 125 episodes."
  ]
}